What you need to know:  Ms Cherop said maternity leave had made her concentrate so much on motherhood making her to add a lot of weight, which she has thoroughly worked and reduced from 66 to 44 kilograms.The cosmetic shop manager Joseph Kemboi said they were elated by her win and they decided to surprise her.“We wanted to congratulate her for the job well done because she has been working very hard in her training. This was a way of saying thank you for her consistency in whatever she does,” he said.